---
title: Supergreen Creamy Pesto Chicken Risoni with Courgette & Green Beans
description: Get ready to savour the ultimate comfort dish with a fresh twist! This green and keen risoni is a bowl of pure joy, featuring tender chicken, a velvety pesto-infused sauce, and a vibrant medley of greens. Each bite is bursting with flavour, thanks to the aromatic basil pesto and perfectly cooked risoni that soaks up all the creamy goodness. Healthy, hearty, and oh-so-delicious!

